<l>kūṭiya kāmam pirintār varavuḷḷik </l>
<l>kōṭuko ṭēṟumeṉ ṉeñcu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart is rid of its sorrow and swells with rapture to think of my absent lover returning with his love.</l>
